OL,6,FITV Granada Reports entertainment
OL,7,Fcorrespondent Caroline Whitmore spoke
OL,8,Fto a little girl who's got her
OL,9,FHollywood debut in a film she's too
OL,10,Fyoung to see.
OL,12,FAvy Berry is pretty modest about her
OL,13,Frole in a multi-million pound film
OL,14,Fproduction that's being seen all over
OL,15,Fthe globe.
OL,17,FAsked by ITV Granada's entertainment
OL,18,Fcorrespondent Caroline Whitmore if she
OL,19,Fwas nervous about filming 'A Quiet
OL,20,FPlace Day One' she replies: "A bit
OL,21,Fnervous."
