OL,3,CSix-year-old survives stroke then
OL,4,Cstars in Hollywood blockbuster
OL,6,FBut Avy, from Failsworth in Oldham,
OL,7,Fhas had a lot more to be worried about
OL,8,Fin her short life. She had major brain
OL,9,Fsurgery after suffering a stroke, aged
OL,10,Ffour.
OL,12,FHer mother Ferne Collins says: "We
OL,13,Ftook her straight to A&E and if we
OL,14,Fhadn't it could have been a different
OL,15,Fstory really."
OL,17,FShe adds that a stroke in one so young
OL,18,Fis rare, but wants to warn other
OL,19,Fparents it does happen. Avy now has
OL,20,Fregular MRI scans.
