OL,6,FFerne says: "When your child's been
OL,7,Fthrough that, you don't care if she's
OL,8,Fin a film it's more that she's
OL,9,Fhealthy."
OL,11,FSix weeks after recovering Avy got her
OL,12,Fpart in 'A Quiet Place: Day One'
OL,13,Falongside Oscar winner Lupita Nyongo,
OL,14,Fwho an Academy Award for Best
OL,15,FSupporting Actress in '12 Years a
OL,16,FSlave' in 2014.
OL,18,FA woman named Sam finds herself
OL,19,Ftrapped in New York City during the
OL,20,Fearly stages of an invasion by alien
OL,21,Fcreatures with ultra-sensitive hearing.
