OL,4,Cstars in Hollywood blockbuster
OL,6,FOn the first day on set Avy was
OL,7,Fsurrounded by hundreds of 'extras'.
OL,8,FFerne says Avy was the only one
OL,9,Fspeaking in the scene.
OL,11,FDespite appearing alongside an Oscar
OL,12,Fwinner, Avy is more interested in her
OL,13,Fother co-star, namely Schnitzel the
OL,14,Fcat.
OL,16,F"He had a chaperone, and he was a real
OL,17,Fcat and I got to hold him all by
OL,18,Fmyself," says the very proud six year
OL,19,Fold.
