OL,6,FLittle Avy is not allowed to actually
OL,7,Fsee the film because of its 15
OL,8,Fcertificate, her mother says even the
OL,9,Ftrailer frightened her.
OL,11,FShe's also appeared in Chester-based
OL,12,Fsoap Hollyoaks as Scott Drinkwell's
OL,13,Ffoster daughter Miley Carson.
OL,15,FIt is clear from what she has achieved
OL,16,Fand overcome in six years that there
OL,17,Fis much more to come for little Avy
OL,18,FBerry.
